data.description: Light & bright! Gorgeous home loaded with upgrades!  Be sure to ask about a possible assumption!  5 Star HRS Energy rating*extensive laminate hardwood flooring* Upgraded cabinetry with pullouts in lower* Granite kitchen counters & large island* Upgraded Stainless Steel Appliances* 3 bedrooms and a great loft upstairs* Window blinds and Curtains all stay! *Laundryroom and separate mudroom ready for your unique touch on the main level *Upgraded fixtures* Upgraded lighting, door & hardware Packages* Ceilings including Tray in the master, living room & loft* Gorgeous upgraded tile floors* Central A/C* Xeriscaped low care & low water landscaping, custom paver patio & stacked stone, with drip system.  For energy conscious buyers this lovely home has a HERS energy rating of 64.  There is  a large crawl space for additional storage* Spacious closets and large kitchen pantry* Enjoy the incredible Banning Lewis experience offering an unmatched lifestyle with fabulous amenities. Your low HOA dues include a membership  to the Rec Center with Pool/Splash Park/Tennis Courts, fitness room and more, plus your trash is included! Plenty of walking & biking trails and free concerts in the park plus a summer farmers market. Easy access to Peterson AFB, the Powers entertainment/shopping corridor and I-25. What a fabulous area to call home!  Don't miss this fantastic home!
